channel.title: Slayer's Fake Gallery
channel.description:
[center]Slayer's fake Gallery![/center]
UPDATE:Since I feel posting daily on seperate threads is spamming the forum, this is now where I will put my daily fakes! Check back for fun and amazement every day!
My first Animation!! Check it out! [url=http://www.imagekafe.com/image.php?image=62a8a.gif]http://www.imagekafe.com/image.php?image=62a8a.gif[/url] And my way cool second one! [url=http://www.imagekafe.com/image.php?image=64575.gif]http://www.imagekafe.com/image.php?image=64575.gif[/url]
One of my first fakes ever, this is my first attempt to make runescape night Oh, and since its kinda hard to see, standing on the parapet is the king, surveying his kingdom, and looking to the ocean. ^_^
[url=http://img59.imageshack.us/my.php?image=kingdom5nt.png][img]http://img59.imageshack.us/img59/8643/kingdom5nt.th.png[/img][/url]
Here's an impressionist painting version of it [url=http://img323.imageshack.us/my.php?image=kingdompainting7et.png][img]http://img323.imageshack.us/img323/2168/kingdompainting7et.th.png[/img][/url]
My first attempt at making runescape daytime [url=http://img472.imageshack.us/my.php?image=sunnywaterfinal27tf.png][img]http://img472.imageshack.us/img472/4152/sunnywaterfinal27tf.th.png[/img][/url]
A better attempt at photo flare and runescape daytime [url=http://img87.imageshack.us/my.php?image=runeglare3ff.png][img]http://img87.imageshack.us/img87/4166/runeglare3ff.th.png[/img][/url]
One of my more recent fakes in which I made RuneScape rainy! [url=http://img524.imageshack.us/my.php?image=runerain24nf.png][img]http://img524.imageshack.us/img524/4246/runerain24nf.th.png[/img][/url]
Another fake in which you see the Lord of the Sun (Jesus maybe?)!! [url=http://img257.imageshack.us/my.php?image=sunlord20ty.png][img]http://img257.imageshack.us/img257/1501/sunlord20ty.th.png[/img][/url]
The Lord of the Sun is so powerful, he can command large stars to overtake the darkness with light! [url=http://img137.imageshack.us/my.php?image=lordstar27py.png][img]http://img137.imageshack.us/img137/8045/lordstar27py.th.png[/img][/url]
Oh no, RuneScape's first hurricane is coming in!!!! Duck and cover!!!! [url=http://img106.imageshack.us/my.php?image=runehurricane27zt.png][img]http://img106.imageshack.us/img106/9026/runehurricane27zt.th.png[/img][/url]
Finally, realistic water reflections!!!! [url=http://img126.imageshack.us/my.php?image=ripple11of.png][img]http://img126.imageshack.us/img126/7923/ripple11of.th.png[/img][/url]
Taking a break from my usual weather reflections, I felt the need to do something(s) funny ^_^ (P.S. In order for it to make sense, open the following two in order)
[url=http://img104.imageshack.us/my.php?image=jump14ix.png][img]http://img104.imageshack.us/img104/6456/jump14ix.th.png[/img][/url] [url=http://img104.imageshack.us/my.php?image=jump20uz.png][img]http://img104.imageshack.us/img104/2005/jump20uz.th.png[/img][/url]
And....I was bored again special thanks to my friend Buffboyf50
[url=http://img104.imageshack.us/my.php?image=varrockbank4id.png][img]http://img104.imageshack.us/img104/9123/varrockbank4id.th.png[/img][/url]
Sir Tiffy goes swimming!
[url=http://img119.imageshack.us/my.php?image=swimming2uf.png][img]http://img119.imageshack.us/img119/5746/swimming2uf.th.png[/img][/url]
[center] :Credits: To my great friends, Jesse, Tim and Zach, for all their support To Microsoft Imaging Suite 10 To The Gimp 2 To Macromedia Fireworks The Print Screen button (Sorry Beret It was just too true and funny to leave off) .......And anyone or anything else I forgot I'm truly sorry [/center]
